<div class="sidebar-list mw-collapsible mw-collapsed"><div class="sidebar-list-title">Adaptations</div><div class="sidebar-list-content mw-collapsible-content"><div class="hlist">
<ul><li><a href="/wiki/List_of_films_of_the_Church_of_Jesus_Christ_of_Latter-day_Saints#Book_of_Mormon_Videos" title="List of films of the Church of Jesus Christ of Latter-day Saints">List of Book of Mormon Videos</a></li>
<li><i><a href="/wiki/How_Rare_a_Possession" title="How Rare a Possession">How Rare a Possession</a></i></li>
<li><i><a href="/wiki/The_Book_of_Mormon_Movie" title="The Book of Mormon Movie">The Book of Mormon Movie</a></i></li>
<li><i><a href="/wiki/Passage_to_Zarahemla" title="Passage to Zarahemla">Passage to Zarahemla</a></i></li>
<li><a href="/wiki/List_of_Book_of_Mormon_translations" title="List of Book of Mormon translations">Translations</a></li></ul>
</div></div></div></td>
</tr><tr><td class="sidebar-content">
<div class="sidebar-list mw-collapsible mw-collapsed"><div class="sidebar-list-title">Other</div><div class="sidebar-list-content mw-collapsible-content"><div class="hlist">
